      <title>土耳其财富基金考虑收购 LetterOne 的 Turkcell 股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/turkey-s-wealth-fund-weighs-buying-letterone-s-stake-in-turkcell</link>
