    <item>
      <title>特朗普为何赦免“丝绸之路”创始人罗斯·乌布利希</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/who-is-ross-ulbricht-the-silk-road-founder-pardoned-by-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统上任第二天就对暗网市场丝绸之路创始人罗斯·乌布利希特颁布了全面赦免令。特朗普在竞选期间曾承诺释放乌布利希特，这是他向加密货币社区做出的一系列承诺之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/who-is-ross-ulbricht-the-silk-road-founder-pardoned-by-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 10:52:57 GMT</pubDate>
